==English==
===Noun===
'''slavery''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

# The use of [[slave]]s to get work done.
# The condition of being enslaved as a slave.
# A condition which is figuratively as bad as slavery.
#: ''Man seeks for gold in mines, that he may weave \ A lasting chain for his own slavery;'' -- Percy Shelley.

